ported in the microwave\nregime. Finally, we also demonstrate fast measurement-free preparation of\nlogical states for the binomial and Gottesman-Kitaev-Preskill (GKP) quantum\nerror-correcting codes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2021 19:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 02:33:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-02"}
