rix of convergent $q$-series with integer coefficients\nand the other studying its Habiro-like arithmetic properties in more depth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Nov 2021 10:24:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 23 Apr 2023 05:27:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-25"}
