 modalities, with the advantage of a high performance. The phase\nspace file implementation was validated and is compatible with the IAEA\nstandard, allowing multiscale Monte Carlo simulations with a combination of CPU\nand GPU codes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Nov 2021 11:46:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-06"}
