 find that\na combination of DR2 and Earth-based astrometry results in dramatically reduced\nuncertainties and, by extension, significantly improved results in comparison\nto those computed based on less accurate Earth-based astrometry alone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Nov 2021 12:48:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-02"}
